div.p:
And this day the King is apparrelled three times, and in
ſeveral ſorts; 1. As a Prieſt; 2. As a King, and a Warrier;
3. As a Judge.

div.head:
Louys 2. to the prejudice of his elder brethren;
and his baſtards to the prejudice of his
lawful ſons.

The Pope is to obey the Determination of the
Common-wealth, without further inquiſition;
except it be in Caſes of injuſtice,
and Tyranny.

div.p:
This Affair will not be ended by any poſſibilitie moral


without ſome War, at leaſt wiſe, for ſome time at the beginning;
and that for divers Reaſons.
